We are looking for a passionate and meticulous Business Development Associate to support potential business development pursuits to achieve business production/partnership. He/she is able to identify cross-selling opportunities and delivers proposals to potential prospects. The Business Development Associate builds his relationship network with industry players and clients, building their confidence through his demonstration of specialist knowledge.

The ideal candidate should be pro-active and possesses strong interpersonal, communication and presentation skills. His core role is to be able to manage customer relations, build up his clientele portfolio and provide business financial advisory and solutions to clients.

*Fresh graduates are welcome to apply*